\par
"And are you learning?"\par
\par
"Maybe." She traced her fingers over the ogham carving, and for a moment, just a moment, felt them tingle with heat.\par
\par
"What does Jude want to be?"\par
\par
"That's too general a question, with too many simple answers like happy, healthy, successful."\par
\par
"Aren't you happy?"\par
\par
